%^BOLD%^-=%^BOLD%^%^RED%^Fire Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

The fire domain draws purely upon the power of elemental 
fire.  As such, it has many of the unpredictible and 
destructive aspects that normal fire does.

The fire domain contains the following spells:
Fire Shield (3rd), Handfire (5th), and Flameburst (7th)

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Jarmila, Ryorik

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
     